node.text:
A journey long from home. “Home is behind, the world ahead, and there are many paths to tread, through shadows to the edge of night, until the stars are all alight.”
cc: @ronald_soethje, @williampatino_photography, @danielw_official, @formgestalter and @moners, @marziopessoa, @cam_snaps
Humans still have a way to go☄️🪩🌌💎
Maravillosa voz 😍 y que imágenes tan hermosas
This is Scotland not New Zealand
My god I wish this was on Spotify 😍 gorgeous voice!
@blaxphoto use this audio with a clip of yours 🥰

This is beautiful, yes. But I don’t see the credit to Billy Boyd who wrote this on the spot, sang & performed this song perfectly on the first take/recording. For anyone who didn’t know it’s origins, now you know. :)
@lupeg117 Hauntingly beautiful and ethereal singing here from our favorite series... Pippin's song always hits home for me! ❤️

user.full_name: Patrick • Nature ⛰️ • Travel 🗺️ • Forest 🌲 from Germany 🇩🇪
